<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="drink-v">drink <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /drɪŋk/    美 /drɪŋk/  </p>
<p>(drank, drunk)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>喝；喝 (酒)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>drink</strong> hard / <strong>heavily</strong> 
酗酒</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She wants to drink juice. 
她要喝果汁。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They drank themselves stupid. 
他们喝得晕头转向。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Don't <strong>drink and drive</strong>.
切勿酒后驾车。</p></div>

<p>注: “喝水”要说drink water；用汤匙“喝汤”要 说eat soup，用杯子“喝汤”用drink soup；“吃药”要说take medicine。  </p>
<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="drink-sbs-health">drink sb’s health</h3>
<p>1.<strong>为某人的健康干杯</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="drink-to-sb-sth">drink to sb / sth</h3>
<p>1.<strong>为某人 / 某事干杯：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Let's drink to your success in your new job.
让我们为你在新工作中取得成功而干杯。</p></div></div>